<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL28">
<l>umparā laṟiya lākā voḷiyuḷā rāṉaik kākic</l>
<l>cempulā luṇṭu vāḻum mutalaimēṟ cīṟi vantār</l>
<l>nampara māya tuṇṭē nāykaḷōm ciṟumai yōrā</l>
<l>empirāṟ kāṭcey yātē eṉceyvāṉ tōṉṟi ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The resplendent [Lord] who cannot be known by the celestials</l>
<l>came swelling with rage for the crocodile—which lives by eating red meat—</l>
<l>for the sake of the elephant.</l>
<l>Is there anything that is a burden for us?</l>
<l>What have I been born for,</l>
<l rend="indent">not serving our Lord who does not consider the baseness of us dogs?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
